===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Rosa (Masters)}}
Rosa, who is based on the [[player character]], forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Snivy}} and its evolved forms {{p|Servine}} and {{p|Serperior}}, along with {{p|Delibird}}, {{form|Shaymin|Sky Forme}} {{p|Shaymin}}, {{p|Dewott}}, {{p|Meloetta}}, and {{form|Deerling|Spring or Summer Form}} {{p|Deerling}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Rosa became a playable sync pair since the game's release, with her joining the {{player}} after completing the first chapter of the [[PML arc]].

Rosa has also made notable appearances in the game's main stories, the PML arc, and the [[villain arc]].

